{"tid":1580961,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城Online］劍士戰法分析","createTime":"2019-09-19T10:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:21:50.000Z","uid":313248,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cafe6b3f7fc6add42632aac179684052b9690355","tid":1580961,"uid":313248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"最近哥布林橫行，仆街GM又收埋咗個PVP保護。我哋唔學一啲<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">近身戰法</span></span>傍身點得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先，一切請以自身<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">保命不被捕</span></span>爲前提。<br />\n自私講句，救人前都請先顧掂自己，唔好到時人又救唔到，重送埋自己頭。<br />\n要救人都好，記得先<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">約人打波</span></span>，提高勝算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二，評估風險。戰前就要判斷打唔打得過，唔得就迴避<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n1）敵眾我寡 &rarr; <span style=\"color: red;\">迴避</span><br />\n2）敵方擁有致命武器 &rarr; <span style=\"color: red;\">迴避</span><br />\n<br />\n以上兩種情況應該唔使特別解釋，不過重有下面一個：<br />\n3）敵方<span style=\"color: red;\">武器等級</span>比你高 &rarr; <span style=\"color: red;\">迴避</span><br />\n<br />\n何謂等級高？記得之前有黃狗喺公務員Secrets提到警察守則嘅時候話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<blockquote>「如果對方用拳，你就用警棍；對方用刀，你就用槍」(類似啦)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個思路確保你（相對地）安全戰鬥。點判斷武器等級，我相信因素其一係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攻擊距離</span></span> (reach)。以下例子顯示攻擊距離嘅重要性：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VamqdoN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVamqdoN.gif&h=de506c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實啲考慮，一般雙方用嘅都係近戰武器，而且雙方武術基礎係0，噉你哋鬥嘅就係攻擊距離。<br />\n對面幾大隻，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">埋唔到你身都冇用</span></span>。所以你見721啲哥布林個個揸藤條長遮，就係為咗拉距離唔俾人還手。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4M0a8Xr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4M0a8Xr.jpg&h=c4cd4611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n常見兵器中，攻擊距離優勢大致：拳 &lt; 縮骨遮 &lt; 長遮<br />\n<br />\n衹要你隨手揸起一樣嘢，你就可以成為劍士。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">長遮</span></span>係無課金玩家最強嘅近戰武器，因為佢有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">攻擊距離</span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔容易俾GM捉</span></span>，重可以幫人<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擋雨</span></span>𠻹。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後補充一篇文章，幫助重未突破心理關口嘅你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n《叔敖斬蛇．豈是私了》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/alfredlgj/posts/10157750394976579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Falfredlgj%2Fposts%2F10157750394976579&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5bTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=6c9a9db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/alfredlgj/posts/10157750394976579</a><br />\n<br />\n第一次開po，1999 sor。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3effe34a4b74058dae1e459c738357c21ed8c5a6","tid":1580961,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T10:18:05.000Z","msg":"【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5bTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=6717c7dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"03303bbf2c1ac38602c908e3503dbb23c3d4be5b","tid":1580961,"uid":313248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T10:20:17.000Z","msg":"祝各位武運昌隆！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1176d54dac9a091db20eacef185a75af582f6dc3","tid":1580961,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T10:21:53.000Z","msg":"基本技能<br />\n每個人都要學"},{"pid":"233c05de28e8859bd3cbd31e2a842f4fbabc0ae9","tid":1580961,"uid":12182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8917924791adeeca2f5842ea55806371a95e4bb","tid":1580961,"uid":313248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"233c05de28e8859bd3cbd31e2a842f4fbabc0ae9","tid":1580961,"uid":12182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"淨係留個emoji重不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595bc670b7e412fdf5a78d922ca27e8f9a7688cf","tid":1580961,"uid":12182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8917924791adeeca2f5842ea55806371a95e4bb","tid":1580961,"uid":313248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"233c05de28e8859bd3cbd31e2a842f4fbabc0ae9","tid":1580961,"uid":12182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.